			<ns0:name>mseaborn@chromium.org</ns0:name><ns0:uri>/u/mseaborn@chromium.org/</ns0:uri></ns0:author><ns0:content type="html">The NaCl GCC toolchain builds uploads a .sha1 hash file next to every tarball it uploads to GSD.  Can we make the PNaCl toolchain build do the same?

This would be really useful when updating the PNaCl toolchain revision in Chromium's DEPS file.  Currently, updating the hashes in DEPS requires downloading all of the PNaCl tarballs, for Linux 32/64-bit and Mac, which takes longer than the normal toolchain download.
